The paper deals with a task that involves combining computer vision, natural language processing, and navigation in a 3D environment. This suggests that it could belong to several sub-categories, including computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and robotics (cs.RO). Among these, computer vision and artificial intelligence seem to be the most relevant, followed by natural language processing and machine learning. Robotics is less likely, as the paper does not focus on physical robots but rather on virtual agents.
